    "## Exercise 1: Vector Operations / ベクトル演算\n",
    "\n",
    "Given two vectors $\\vec{u} = [1, 2, 3]$ and $\\vec{v} = [4, 5, 6]$, compute:\n",
    "\n",
    "2つのベクトル $\\vec{u} = [1, 2, 3]$ と $\\vec{v} = [4, 5, 6]$ について、以下を計算してください：\n",
    "\n",
    "1. The sum $\\vec{u} + \\vec{v}$ / ベクトルの和\n",
    "2. The dot product $\\vec{u} \\cdot \\vec{v}$ / 内積\n",
    "3. The magnitude (norm) of $\\vec{u}$ / $\\vec{u}$ の大きさ（ノルム）\n",
    "4. The angle between them in degrees / 2つのベクトル間の角度（度）"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 3,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Sum / 和: [5 7 9]\n",
      "Dot product / 内積: 32\n",
      "Norm of u / u のノルム: 3.7416573867739413\n",
      "Angle / 角度: 12.933154491899135 degrees\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "u = np.array([1, 2, 3])\n",
    "v = np.array([4, 5, 6])\n",
    "\n",
    "## Your code here / ここにコードを書いてください\n",
    "vector_sum = u + v\n",
    "dot_product = np.dot(u, v)\n",
    "norm_u = np.linalg.norm(u)\n",
    "angle_degrees = np.degrees(np.arccos(np.dot(u, v) / (np.linalg.norm(u) * np.linalg.norm(v))))\n",
    "\n",
    "print('Sum / 和:', vector_sum)\n",
    "print('Dot product / 内積:', dot_product)\n",
    "print('Norm of u / u のノルム:', norm_u)\n",
    "print('Angle / 角度:', angle_degrees, 'degrees')"
   ]
  },
  {
