    "## Exercise 2: Matrix Transpose / 行列の転置\n",
    "\n",
    "Write a function `my_transpose(A)` that returns the transpose of matrix $A$ **without using** `np.transpose` or `.T`.\n",
    "\n",
    "`np.transpose` や `.T` を**使わずに**、行列 $A$ の転置を返す関数 `my_transpose(A)` を書いてください。\n",
    "\n",
    "Hint / ヒント: $A^T[i][j] = A[j][i]$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Original / 元の行列: [[1, 2, 3], [4, 5, 6]]\n",
      "Transpose / 転置: [[1, 4], [2, 5], [3, 6]]\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def my_transpose(A):\n",
    "    ## Your code here / ここにコードを書いてください\n",
    "    rows = len(A)\n",
    "    cols = len(A[0])\n",
    "    return [[A[j][i] for j in range(rows)] for i in range(cols)]\n",
    "\n",
    "# Test / テスト\n",
    "A = [[1, 2, 3],\n",
    "     [4, 5, 6]]\n",
    "print('Original / 元の行列:', A)\n",
    "print('Transpose / 転置:', my_transpose(A))\n",
    "# Expected / 期待される結果: [[1, 4], [2, 5], [3, 6]]"
   ]
  },
  {
