    "## Exercise 6: Linear Transformation / 線形変換\n",
    "\n",
    "A linear transformation $T: \\mathbb{R}^3 \\to \\mathbb{R}^2$ is defined by:\n",
    "\n",
    "線形変換 $T: \\mathbb{R}^3 \\to \\mathbb{R}^2$ を以下のように定義します：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$T\\left(\\begin{bmatrix} x_1 \\\\ x_2 \\\\ x_3 \\end{bmatrix}\\right) = \\begin{bmatrix} x_1 - 2x_2 + x_3 \\\\ 3x_1 + x_2 - x_3 \\end{bmatrix}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "1. Find the standard matrix representation of $T$ / $T$ の標準行列表示を求めてください\n",
    "2. Determine if $T$ is **onto** (surjective) / $T$ が**全射**であるか判定してください\n",
    "3. Determine if $T$ is **one-to-one** (injective) / $T$ が**単射**であるか判定してください\n",
    "4. Determine if $T$ is **invertible** / $T$ が**可逆**であるか判定してください"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 8,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
